column5: Hey guys and gals, I hope everyone had a safe and fun new year. I was wondering if anyone knew about the ice conditions up in Huntsville. I have a bone to pick with a lake up there and wanted to make a trip soon. PM me if you want to. Thanks
Here in Haliburton, lakes with no current have a solid 6-8". After the rains on the 1st, anyplace with current opened up considerably.
Thanks singingdog, that's what I needed to know.
